    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small chests or boxes for holding objects of value such as money, letters, and jewels; usually of wood or metal and highly ornamented and often hinged.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
